@demographics
go-to: menu

**Demographic Groups**

**Working Class**: The urban working class - blue-collar workers in factories, workshops, mines, and the like. Most are <span style="color: #c00000;">socialists</span>, supporting either the <span style="color: #FFC000;">**Lib Dems**</span> or <span style="color: #700000;">**KPD**</span>. They make up 40-50% of the population.

**Old Mittelstand**: The old middle class consists of independent artisans, shopkeepers, and small-time businesspeople. They tend to be conservative and are the strongest base for the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">far</span>-<span style="color: #3E88B3;">right</span>. 10-15% of the population.

**New Mittelstand**: The new middle class consists of white-collar workers and government employees. This is the base of <span style="color: #D3C24D;">liberalism</span>. 10-15% of the population.

**Rural**: Small and large farmers and independent rural workers. Protestant farmers usually supports the [? if not cvp_formed: <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span>?][? if cvp_formed: <span style="color: #000000;">**[+ z_party_name +]**</span>?]. [? if rural_nsdap_normalized >= 25: However the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Nazis</span> have gained a strong appeal among them?]. 20-30% of the population.

**Catholics** are the largest religious minority, at about 30% of the population. [? if not cvp_formed: They disproportionately support the [? if z_party_name != "CVP": <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span>?][? if z_party_name == "CVP": <span style="color: #000000;">**CVP**</span>?]?][? if cvp_formed: They find themselves split between supporting the <span style="color: #000000;">**CVP**</span> and the <span style="color: #FFC000;">**Lib Dems**</span>. ?] (or the <span style="color: #A2D8E0;">**Bavarian People's Party**</span> in <span style="color: #00CCFF;">Bavaria</span>).

**Jews** account for between 0.5% to 1% of the population, and tend to support liberal parties, [? if ddp_name == "DDP" or not ddp_name: mostly the DDP?][? if ddp_name == "DStP": although the mild antisemitism of the Young German Order and it's association with the <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span> has driven them away?], although substantial numbers support the <span style="color: #FFC000;">**Lib Dems**</span> or <span style="color: #700000;">**KPD**</span>.


